ell and looks well placed to return to winning form. 1. ACAPULCO GIRL finished fifth of 10 at Ipswich last start over this distance after getting held up into the turn. Has a strong record at this distance having scored two of four starts. A bold showing is expected with the blinkers added. 12. BREEZIN' went a solid race when resuming from a spell last start to finish third of 10 over 1110m at this track after getting held up into the straight. Placed to advantage and has to be respected. 5. MERCURIAL LADY after jumping from a wide draw settled well back in the running and then came home strongly into the straight to finish third of 10 over 1200m at this track. Fitter and jumping from a good draw should jump as the favourite and prove hard to beat.\",\"runners\":[11,1,12,5],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,11,4,10]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,5,11,4]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,5,4,1]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,6,1,13]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[14,11,1,5]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,11,4,7]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,11,4,1]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":7,"venueMnemonic":